---
title: Spooky Spiced Burgers with scary sweet potatoes
description: It's no trick! In fact, these cheesy Mexican spiced burgers are really more of a treat. Served with spooky sweet potato faces, this truly is a meal fit for a Halloween feast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W44_IE_IEFP17460-3_Main_ahigh-e5611962.jpg
